Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:00.50,0:00:03.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大家，卡萊多之星要開始了哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:03.50,0:00:06.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,觀看的時候\N要注意保持屋內亮度
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:06.30,0:00:08.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不要離電視太近了哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:11.30,0:00:12.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我叫苗木野空
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:12.50,0:00:15.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為嚮往卡萊多劇團\N獨自一人來到美國
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:15.80,0:00:17.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,雖然遇到各種挑戰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:17.30,0:00:20.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,與其多想還是先做\N比較符合我的性格
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:20.90,0:00:24.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不會放棄正在做的事\N卻總能幸運地完成做不了的事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:24.10,0:00:26.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,必要的時候決不放棄！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:26.40,0:00:27.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就是這麼回事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:29.00,0:00:30.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那麼，那麼，那麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:30.50,0:00:32.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大家聽說過人魚公主嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:32.60,0:00:34.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,非常精彩的故事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:34.50,0:00:37.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我這次必須挑戰的是這個角色
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:37.40,0:00:39.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是失敗之後好害怕
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:39.90,0:00:41.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而且久久不能忘懷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:41.70,0:00:43.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊，這次真的是遇到了大災難了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:34.40,0:02:36.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:36.20,0:02:38.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,午飯拿來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:38.50,0:02:40.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝，瑪莉奧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:40.10,0:02:41.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大家，吃飯了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:49.90,0:02:51.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,今天就坐在這裏吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:54.60,0:02:57.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,今天說的是人魚公主的故事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:57.60,0:03:02.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,很久以前某個地方\N有一位非常漂亮的人魚公主
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:14.40,0:03:18.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,今天的演出就到此結束了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:18.30,0:03:24.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,灰姑娘的公演\N由於舞臺修整將停演一周
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:24.20,0:03:27.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,請各位下周光臨
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:28.40,0:03:29.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,辛苦啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:33.70,0:03:37.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,明天開始終於開始放假了\N真象做夢一樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:37.00,0:03:39.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你們有什麼安排嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:39.00,0:03:40.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,練習啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:40.10,0:03:41.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為了試演做準備哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:42.50,0:03:45.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,假期的最後有試演……
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:45.10,0:03:46.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你不知道嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:46.50,0:03:47.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不知道啊！不知道啊！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:47.70,0:03:49.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼就我不知道呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:49.00,0:03:50.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,宿舍的公告板上都有寫著的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:52.40,0:03:53.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是什麼的呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:53.80,0:03:56.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,去年的劇目今年再演
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:56.90,0:03:58.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,《人魚公主》
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:58.30,0:04:00.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不會吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:00.00,0:04:01.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼啦？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:01.30,0:04:04.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我只看過錄影啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:04.00,0:04:05.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,天哪，是真的啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:05.80,0:04:06.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可以看到真人表演了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:06.90,0:04:07.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好高興
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:07.90,0:04:12.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,特別是最後一幕\N人魚公主從船上跳到海裏
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:12.10,0:04:14.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不管看多少次\N每次都哭的稀哩嘩啦的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:14.30,0:04:15.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好啦好啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:15.60,0:04:19.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這次蕾拉小姐\N要挑戰新的空中飛人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:19.40,0:04:21.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,試演的時候主要考空中飛人的哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:23.50,0:04:24.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是機會哦，空
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:25.80,0:04:27.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是你擅長的強項啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:27.50,0:04:28.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,擅長？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:28.50,0:04:30.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,黃金不死鳥都試過了嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:31.80,0:04:33.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,馬上就可以成為准主角啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:33.80,0:04:35.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:35.20,0:04:36.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要加油了啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:36.70,0:04:38.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,順便也可以多拿點演出費
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:38.60,0:04:40.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真的是哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:40.30,0:04:42.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,每天都有車子接送哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:42.30,0:04:44.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可以嗎？要人接送
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:45.30,0:04:46.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真少見啊！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:46.40,0:04:48.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,自說自話的傢伙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:48.40,0:04:50.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真是討厭
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:54.10,0:04:58.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,然後人魚公主\N為了得到人類的樣子……
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:01.10,0:05:02.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:05.80,0:05:07.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,演出的準備怎麼樣了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:07.80,0:05:09.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,進行的很順利
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:09.70,0:05:11.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯，很好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:11.50,0:05:15.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我太忙了，現在就想看看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:15.60,0:05:18.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,試演的預定時間是二周後
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:18.30,0:05:21.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,囉嗦，我現在就要看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:21.70,0:05:25.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不要對我說什麼\N“現在不能看”之類的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:25.30,0:05:28.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不，我表演的劇目\N現在馬上就可以開始
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:29.40,0:05:31.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你對我有什麼不滿嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:31.50,0:05:34.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不，你是非常優秀的明星
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:34.20,0:05:36.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這點我很清楚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:36.80,0:05:41.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是這裏除了蕾拉以外\N就沒有明星了嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:41.40,0:05:43.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這個人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:43.30,0:05:46.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有點象人魚公主裏面\N跑出來的魔法師嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:49.10,0:05:50.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼樣呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:54.10,0:05:57.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這次試演的場地比較特別
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:58.30,0:05:59.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果成功通過試演
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:59.80,0:06:02.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,立刻就可以參加人魚公主的演出
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:02.20,0:06:07.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是失敗的話\N將取消人魚公主的出演資格
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:07.80,0:06:10.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有人想要試一試嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:10.50,0:06:12.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,失敗的話就要退出了啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:12.40,0:06:14.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真是糟糕了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:14.30,0:06:16.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有人要來試試看嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:16.40,0:06:19.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這個人魚公主怎麼樣？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:19.00,0:06:20.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,主角哦～主角～
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:21.20,0:06:22.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,主角啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:23.10,0:06:24.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼啦？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:24.80,0:06:25.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,決定了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:26.30,0:06:27.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,空
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:27.10,0:06:28.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,現在就由你來演人魚公主
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:30.20,0:06:33.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是人魚公主\N不是蕾拉小姐的角色嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:33.00,0:06:34.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有什麼不好的嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:34.20,0:06:36.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,剛才不還說很擅長空中飛人的嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:36.60,0:06:38.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還很自信的樣子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:40.50,0:06:44.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而且還說得到這個角色的話\N演出費將是現在的十倍什麼的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:44.80,0:06:46.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還可以\N去南方的島嶼旅行什麼的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:47.40,0:06:48.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,原來如此
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:48.50,0:06:50.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,既然你已經有了那些計畫
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:50.90,0:06:52.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就不得不演人魚公主了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:26.90,0:07:28.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,準備好了嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:28.20,0:07:29.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:29.50,0:07:30.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,健
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:30.50,0:07:31.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,該怎麼做？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:31.90,0:07:33.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不用擔心，空
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:33.50,0:07:35.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,現在就解釋表演內容
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:36.50,0:07:39.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,空只要使用現在這個位置的橫杆
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:39.00,0:07:41.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,跳到對面的橫杆上就可以了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:42.40,0:07:44.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我一按信號器就開始跳
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:45.20,0:07:49.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那樣的話\N恰好可以跳到瀑布對面的橫杆上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:49.70,0:07:50.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,瀑布？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:01.50,0:08:02.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好，開始吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:02.70,0:08:03.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,瞭解
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:03.70,0:08:04.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,開始了哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:05.70,0:08:07.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不用擔心，空很拿手的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:09.90,0:08:11.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什麼不用擔心啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:14.60,0:08:17.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,瀑布擋著\N我看不到對面的橫杆
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:17.10,0:08:18.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼辦？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:21.40,0:08:23.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不，別想了，還是試了再說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:30.90,0:08:31.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,空
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:32.80,0:08:34.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,糟了，晚了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:34.00,0:08:34.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,快回來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:44.90,0:08:45.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好，能過去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:57.60,0:08:58.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:00.00,0:09:02.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊呀，我失敗了？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:08.10,0:09:09.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不行了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:33.00,0:09:35.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,太好了，你醒了啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:35.50,0:09:37.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是你救了我？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:37.40,0:09:38.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:38.50,0:09:39.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看樣子你沒什麼要緊了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:40.90,0:09:43.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是的，謝謝你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:43.50,0:09:44.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那麼我走了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:47.00,0:09:49.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你去哪里？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:50.50,0:09:53.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們的城堡——卡萊多劇團
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:53.20,0:09:54.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我也去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:55.60,0:09:56.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你不能來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:57.80,0:10:02.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為什……
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:02.10,0:10:04.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你不能來我們的世界
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:04.90,0:10:07.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,回去你自己的世界吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:08.40,0:10:12.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,等一下，請等一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:12.20,0:10:14.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,等一下，等等
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:14.90,0:10:15.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,等一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:18.50,0:10:19.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,醒了？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:20.50,0:10:22.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哦，精神很不錯啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:23.60,0:10:24.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,太好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:25.50,0:10:26.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼啦？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:26.90,0:10:29.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,痛痛痛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:29.60,0:10:32.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,別太勉強了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:32.10,0:10:35.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,雖然是輕傷，不過也脫臼了呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:35.10,0:10:37.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是如果沒有由利的話\N就不止是脫臼而已了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:39.50,0:10:43.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,千鈞一髮的時候\N是由利救了你哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:43.70,0:10:46.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我還是第一次\N看見真人的人工呼吸呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:49.20,0:10:51.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那個原來是真的啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:51.30,0:10:53.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你知道嘛，健看到了啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:53.30,0:10:55.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是啊，是啊，健呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:55.70,0:10:57.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,健啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:01.00,0:11:02.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,空，你在幹嗎呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:03.60,0:11:04.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:04.70,0:11:06.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,“啊”什麼呀？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:06.50,0:11:08.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,別太勉強了，空
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:08.10,0:11:10.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還沒得到醫生的同意吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:10.00,0:11:11.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒問題了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:11.70,0:11:13.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不快點給贊助商看表演的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:13.30,0:11:14.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可能就無法演出了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:19.30,0:11:19.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:20.90,0:11:23.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊呀，怎麼了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:23.40,0:11:25.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊呀，啊呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:25.70,0:11:28.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊呀，好奇怪啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:28.00,0:11:29.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:33.50,0:11:35.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,空
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:35.60,0:11:36.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你沒事吧，空
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:38.80,0:11:40.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,空，別太勉強了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:41.90,0:11:42.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯，對不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:43.30,0:11:45.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,今天好像精神不太好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:45.60,0:11:47.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我先回去休息了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:47.60,0:11:48.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,等一下，空
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:48.90,0:11:50.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:50.10,0:11:51.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,老實的告訴我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:52.40,0:11:54.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,空，難道你是在害怕？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:57.00,0:11:58.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真的是這樣嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:59.90,0:12:01.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,空，要是害怕的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:01.60,0:12:03.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,別管我，我沒事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:04.70,0:12:06.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一定要馬上阻止她
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:06.10,0:12:07.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,空也真是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:08.50,0:12:09.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,空
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:10.70,0:12:11.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼啦？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:34.00,0:12:35.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼樣了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:35.40,0:12:37.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,總之，可以讓我們再試一次
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:38.60,0:12:40.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,接下來的事就看主演了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:42.30,0:12:43.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,空
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:43.40,0:12:44.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喂，空
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:45.40,0:12:46.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,去吃飯了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:47.30,0:12:50.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不吃晚飯的話，傷不會很快好的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:51.20,0:12:53.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不用管我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:53.60,0:12:55.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真是丟人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:55.30,0:12:56.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好囉嗦啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:56.80,0:12:59.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼今天偷懶沒去練習？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:59.10,0:13:01.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我受傷了嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:01.00,0:13:02.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼躲在裏面不出來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:02.70,0:13:03.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,肩膀痛嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:03.90,0:13:04.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:04.50,0:13:06.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,行了，別管我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:07.80,0:13:09.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,和那個時候一樣啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:10.50,0:13:11.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那個時候？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:11.40,0:13:14.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,曾經也有個\N能看見我樣子的男孩
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:14.50,0:13:17.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,之後他因為受傷不能再跳了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:17.50,0:13:20.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,傷好以後\N因為害怕再也上不了台了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:21.10,0:13:23.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,上不了台了嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:23.00,0:13:24.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:28.10,0:13:29.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼做？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:29.10,0:13:31.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼做才能不害怕？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:31.00,0:13:33.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哦，果然和受傷沒有關係啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:33.80,0:13:35.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,行了，該怎麼做？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:35.40,0:13:36.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,告訴我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:39.90,0:13:41.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這個是？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:41.10,0:13:42.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,被吊的男人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:42.90,0:13:43.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,空
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:43.70,0:13:47.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果你想改變現在的情形\N就不能逃避
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:47.50,0:13:49.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我沒有逃避……
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:49.40,0:13:54.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那個人漸漸的再也看不見我了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:10.50,0:14:12.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這是？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:12.20,0:14:13.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,空
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:13.20,0:14:14.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,健
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:14.50,0:14:16.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,果然讓我猜對了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:16.00,0:14:17.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,空還是回來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:17.80,0:14:20.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,健，剛才對不起了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:20.60,0:14:21.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:22.30,0:14:24.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我根本沒在意那個
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:24.00,0:14:27.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還是練習重要吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:27.00,0:14:29.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,想著你可能會回來\N我準備了這個
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:29.70,0:14:31.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為我準備的？這個？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:31.90,0:14:35.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是的，為了讓你練習準備的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:35.50,0:14:36.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為了我？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:36.70,0:14:41.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯，剛才沒有考慮到空的心情
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:41.40,0:14:44.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不，是我不好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:44.30,0:14:48.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是這麼低的橫杆不能練習吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:48.00,0:14:50.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不，正因為低了可以慢慢地成功
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:50.80,0:14:53.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這樣你就可以有完整的印象了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:53.90,0:14:55.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,完整的印象？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:55.30,0:15:00.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是的，練到你忘了失敗的事為止
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:00.00,0:15:03.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這麼說的話不是太簡單了？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:03.40,0:15:04.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這個主意怎麼樣？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:10.00,0:15:12.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這樣不行啊，健
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:12.00,0:15:14.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這也是為了讓空\N能有個成功的印象啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:14.40,0:15:16.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是……
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:16.00,0:15:17.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我會提醒你跳的時機
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:17.80,0:15:19.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,按照我的暗號提示來跳
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:24.60,0:15:26.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好了嗎，空，要開始了哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:26.80,0:15:28.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,忘了失敗的事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:28.30,0:15:30.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,集中精神配合我的提示
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:38.10,0:15:39.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,開始了哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:39.80,0:15:42.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,1，2，3……
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:52.90,0:15:54.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒事吧，空
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:54.20,0:15:56.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不行，對不起，健
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:56.40,0:15:58.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:58.30,0:16:00.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,空，振作點
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:00.00,0:16:01.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我做不到
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:01.60,0:16:03.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,空，看著我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:03.20,0:16:05.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,拜託了，相信我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:05.70,0:16:08.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我一定會幫助你成功的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:08.90,0:16:11.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,雖然我不能象由利那樣救你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:11.50,0:16:13.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是我一定要幫你\N成為人魚公主
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:14.50,0:16:15.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,空
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:16.40,0:16:17.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我明白了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:17.80,0:16:19.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝你，健
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:19.70,0:16:20.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那麼再來一次
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:31.50,0:16:32.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這個……
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:33.50,0:16:36.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這位是功夫大師林老師
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:36.60,0:16:39.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,老師是專門研究精神統一的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:39.60,0:16:42.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,來幫助你提高集中力的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:43.90,0:16:44.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,快點照做啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:46.50,0:16:49.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,林老師要測試你一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:53.50,0:16:54.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果你能夠跟著做的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:54.60,0:16:57.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就教你身心統一的方法
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:58.20,0:16:59.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是，請多關照
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:08.50,0:17:10.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,測試合格了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:10.20,0:17:10.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,已經……？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:21.70,0:17:24.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對了，就象那樣放鬆心情
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:28.30,0:17:29.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒關係，再來一次
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:41.00,0:17:42.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還是做不好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:42.70,0:17:44.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒那回事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:44.30,0:17:48.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,林老師對於你的進步很讚賞啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:58.00,0:18:00.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那個是精神統一的絕招
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:00.60,0:18:01.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好厲害啊，空
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:01.90,0:18:04.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,居然能夠看到這種絕招
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:04.20,0:18:05.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喂，還傻愣著幹嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:05.50,0:18:06.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,快點，你也照做啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:11.60,0:18:15.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,與自然和為一體\N將身心託付自然
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:15.20,0:18:19.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那麼你就能成為風\N成為水，成為大地
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:19.10,0:18:21.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,和周圍的一切成為一體
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:21.70,0:18:25.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這就是精神統一的奧義
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:29.60,0:18:30.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,空
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:34.00,0:18:36.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,將身心託付自然
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:36.20,0:18:38.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要休息一會嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:38.00,0:18:39.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不，沒關係
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:39.90,0:18:41.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還差一點就完成了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:45.60,0:18:46.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:46.70,0:18:48.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,已經差不多了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:49.10,0:18:51.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還是等傷完全好了比較好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:51.70,0:18:54.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,醫生說你的傷已經沒事了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:55.60,0:18:57.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,難道說你是在害怕？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:59.10,0:19:00.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果不能跳的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:00.90,0:19:02.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你就沒有繼續留在這裏的意義了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:19.80,0:19:22.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你就沒有繼續留在這裏的意義了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:23.00,0:19:24.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,冷靜點，空
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:24.00,0:19:25.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不用太擔心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:25.90,0:19:27.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:27.30,0:19:28.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼能這麼說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:30.10,0:19:32.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你不是一直在努力地練習嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:32.90,0:19:34.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就是因為是練習
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:34.10,0:19:35.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就是因為是練習才行的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:36.70,0:19:38.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真正試的時候肯定不行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:39.20,0:19:41.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不能跳了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:41.30,0:19:43.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,肯定
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:43.80,0:19:45.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不能再跳了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:45.30,0:19:46.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你這輩子都打算不再跳了嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:48.60,0:19:53.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,當我得知因自己的心臟\N過於衰弱而不能再跳的時候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:53.30,0:19:54.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那時的心情至今記憶猶新
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:55.70,0:19:57.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,想跳卻跳不了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:57.90,0:19:59.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就象現在的你一樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:59.70,0:20:01.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是你還是行的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:03.10,0:20:05.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,練習黃金不死鳥的時候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:05.80,0:20:07.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,雖然練習很辛苦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:07.30,0:20:10.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可我總覺得無論如何也要試試
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:11.20,0:20:14.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,卡萊多劇團裏優秀的人雖然很多
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:14.30,0:20:16.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,能讓我那麼想要躍躍欲試的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:16.80,0:20:17.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,空還是第一個
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:19.30,0:20:21.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好好回憶一下跳在空中的感覺
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:21.80,0:20:22.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,空
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:27.40,0:20:30.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,跳在空中的感覺
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:30.70,0:20:32.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不要放棄，空
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:32.80,0:20:36.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我會保佑你，不希望你失敗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:43.20,0:20:44.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,空
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:46.70,0:20:47.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝，健
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:56.00,0:20:56.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,空
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:03.70,0:21:05.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,蒙住眼睛？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:05.00,0:21:06.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不要緊嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:06.40,0:21:08.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,當然
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:08.00,0:21:08.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,開始吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:08.80,0:21:10.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,明白
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:10.10,0:21:11.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要開始了，空
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:11.50,0:21:12.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,準備好了嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:15.30,0:21:16.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,去吧，空
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:16.60,0:21:18.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,1，2，3！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:38.80,0:21:42.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不能跳的話你就沒有\N繼續留在這裏的意義了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:43.40,0:21:46.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,與自然和為一體\N將身心託付自然
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:46.90,0:21:48.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,和周圍的一切成為一體
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:48.60,0:21:51.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如此你便能與天空成為一體
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:56.80,0:21:57.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,太精彩了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:06.40,0:22:07.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,太好了，空
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:08.50,0:22:12.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,空在卡萊多眾多明星之中\N果然是最耀眼的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:19.80,0:23:22.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,下集預告：卡萊多之星
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:22.20,0:23:24.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,去吧，空，主角就是你了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:24.20,0:23:26.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就是這麼回事\N我第一次做主角
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:26.70,0:23:29.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,雖然想像蕾拉小姐\N那樣的完美表演
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:29.20,0:23:30.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,客人太挑剔了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:30.90,0:23:33.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,得不到贊助商的幫助了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:33.40,0:23:36.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,到底是哪里不對了呢\N了呢，了呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:37.80,0:23:39.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,下一集：卡萊多之星
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:42.50,0:23:46.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,翅膀是夢想，飛向空
